  "data": {
    "title": "Unitel Voice: Sound Professional Without a Second Phone",
    "excerpt": "Unitel Voice gives your small business a pro phone number, IVR, and extensions on your existing device. See why thousands of builders love it. Try it today.",
    "featured_image": {
      "$media": {
        "url": "https://tonyciencia.com/blog/unitel-voice-tips.jpg",
        "alt": "Unitel Voice: Sound Professional Without a Second Phone",
        "filename": "unitel-voice-tips.jpg"
      }
    },
    "content": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "When I started freelancing three years ago, I did what most people do: I gave out my personal cell number to clients. Big mistake. Within weeks, my phone rang at 10 PM on a Saturday with a \"quick question\" about a project, and my mom's calls got buried between invoices and client updates. It was chaos.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/what-is-unitel-voice"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "That experience taught me something simple but powerful: separating your business life from your personal life starts with your phone number. And the tool that made that separation effortless for me was ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Unitel Voice",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you're a freelancer, consultant, side-hustler, or small team owner still juggling calls on a single personal line, this post is for you. I'll walk you through exactly how Unitel Voice works, the features I rely on daily, and the best ways to squeeze every ounce of value out of this platform.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Why I Switched to a Virtual Phone System (And Why You Should Too)",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here's the thing about modern business: customers expect you to sound legit, even if you're running things from your kitchen table. A generic personal number with a \"Hey, this is Mike\" voicemail doesn't exactly scream reliability.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://unitelvoice.com/?ref=tonyciencia"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Unitel Voice solves that instantly. You get a ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "professional business phone number",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — local or toll-free — that routes to your existing cell phone. No second device, no expensive hardware, no IT guy. Just pick a number, set up your greeting, and you're in business. Literally.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What impressed me from day one was the speed. I signed up, chose a local number with my area code, recorded a quick professional greeting, and had calls forwarding to my cell within 15 minutes. My clients started calling the new number, and suddenly I sounded like I had a full office behind me.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/how-to-use-unitel-voice"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you want the full walkthrough, check out our ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "step-by-step Unitel Voice tutorial",
            "marks": [
              "l2"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " where we cover every setup detail.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Standout Features That Make Unitel Voice Worth It",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've tested a handful of virtual phone platforms over the years, and Unitel Voice stands out because it nails the balance between power and simplicity. You don't need a CS degree to configure it, but you still get features that rival enterprise phone systems.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here's what I use the most:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Professional Phone Number Options",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Choose from local numbers, toll-free numbers (800, 888, 877, etc.), and vanity numbers. I went with a toll-free number for my consulting side gig because it adds that extra layer of credibility. Clients perceive a toll-free line as a sign of an established company — even when you're a team of one.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Auto-Attendant (IVR)",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This is the feature that changed my game. Unitel Voice gives you a full interactive voice response system. You know, the \"Press 1 for Sales, Press 2 for Support\" thing. I set mine up so new callers hear a professional greeting, then get routed to the right extension (which is just my cell phone). It takes 10 minutes to configure and makes you sound like you have a receptionist.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Multiple Extensions",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Even if you're a solo operator, you can create extensions for different roles. I have extensions for \"General Inquiries,\" \"Billing,\" and \"Project Updates.\" In reality, they all ring to my phone — but the caller experience feels polished and organized.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Call Forwarding & Routing",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Forward calls to any phone number. Send them to your cell during work hours, to voicemail after 6 PM, or to a partner's phone when you're on vacation. The scheduling rules are intuitive and flexible.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Voicemail-to-Email",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Every voicemail lands in my inbox as an audio file. I can listen, save, and organize without ever opening the Unitel Voice app. It's a small feature that saves me real time every week.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Business Hours & After-Hours Greetings",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Record different greetings for different times. During business hours, callers hear your live greeting. After hours, they hear a message letting them know you'll return their call the next business day. This one change alone stopped my 11 PM phone interruptions.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Custom Caller ID",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "When you make outbound calls through the system, your business number shows up on the recipient's caller ID — not your personal number. Professional from both directions.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l3",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/unitel-voice-new-features"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For a deep dive into every capability, see our ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "complete Unitel Voice feature breakdown",
            "marks": [
              "l3"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Best Tips for Getting Maximum Value from Unitel Voice",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "After using Unitel Voice for over two years, I've picked up tricks that make it work even harder:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "1. Set Up Your IVR Before You Need It",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Don't wait until you're overwhelmed with calls. Create your auto-attendant tree on day one. Even a simple \"Thanks for calling! Press 1 to leave a message, or stay on the line to reach me directly\" makes a massive difference in how callers perceive your business.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "2. Use Business Hours Scheduling Religiously",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I set strict business hours (Monday–Friday, 9 AM–5 PM). Outside those hours, calls go straight to a custom after-hours greeting. This protects your personal time without missing opportunities — callers know you'll get back to them.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "3. Record Multiple Greetings and A/B Test Them",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've recorded five different greetings over the past two years. The one that mentions my specific service (\"Thanks for calling [Company Name], specializing in digital strategy for small businesses\") converts better than a generic greeting. Every few months, swap it out and see how callers respond.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "4. Create Role-Based Extensions Even as a Solo Business",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Having separate extensions for sales, support, and billing isn't vanity — it helps you understand why someone's calling before you pick up. When your phone rings and you see \"Extension: 3 (Billing),\" you know exactly what to expect.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "5. Use Toll-Free Numbers for Marketing Campaigns",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you're running ads, put a toll-free number on your landing pages. It tracks as a distinct channel and signals trust to cold traffic. Unitel Voice makes it easy to add and manage multiple numbers.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "6. Pair It with Your CRM Workflow",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l4",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/how-to-use-clickup"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I forward voicemails to email, then log them in my ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "project management tool",
            "marks": [
              "l4"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " so nothing falls through the cracks. It's not a native integration, but the email-forwarding workflow makes it seamless.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l5",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/unitel-voice-use-cases"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
