      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Who Is Unitel Voice Ideal For?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Unitel Voice isn't trying to be an enterprise UCaaS platform with 400 features you'll never touch. It's built for people who need a professional phone presence without the complexity or cost. Here's who benefits the most:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Freelancers and Solopreneurs",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — If you're giving out your personal number to clients, Unitel Voice is the fastest upgrade you can make. Professional number, voicemail, and call routing on your existing phone.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Small Teams (2–20 people)",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — Need extensions for each team member? Done. Everyone gets calls routed to their own devices, and you manage it all from a single dashboard.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Side-Hustlers with Day Jobs",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — Use business hours scheduling so your side-gig calls only ring during your available hours. No more awkward calls during meetings at your 9-to-5.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Service-Based Businesses",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — Salons, consultants, real estate agents, accountants, coaches — anyone who books appointments or handles client inquiries over the phone. The auto-attendant alone is worth it.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Remote Teams",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — Your team could be scattered across three time zones, and callers would never know. Everyone sounds like they're in the same office.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Startups Testing the Waters",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — Not ready for a full PBX system? Unitel Voice gives you 80% of the professional image at 10% of the cost. You can always scale up later.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l6",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://unitelvoice.com/?ref=tonyciencia"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If any of these sound like you, ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "go grab a Unitel Voice number and try it out",
            "marks": [
              "l6"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ". Setup takes minutes, not days.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
