      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How Unitel Voice Stacks Up on Pricing",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "One thing I appreciate about Unitel Voice: the pricing is transparent and accessible. Plans start at a price point that makes sense for solo operators, and you won't find nickel-and-dime charges for basic features like voicemail or call forwarding.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Compare that to traditional business phone providers that require contracts, equipment rentals, and installation fees. I spent less on a full year of Unitel Voice than I would on one month of a legacy phone system.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The value is especially clear when you consider what you're replacing: a second phone, a second phone plan, or worse — a clunky on-premise system that requires someone to maintain it. Unitel Voice runs entirely in the cloud. You manage it from your browser or phone. No hardware, no headaches.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l7",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/why-choose-unitel-voice"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Want the full breakdown on why this platform keeps winning fans? Read our detailed ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "why-choose-Unitel-Voice guide",
            "marks": [
              "l7"
            ]
